  "description": "<p>👮‍♂️HIRING FULL TIME BOUTIQUE SECURITY CONCIERGE OFFICERS</p><p>📍Location: Marina Bay Sands (High End Luxury Brand)</p><p>💰Salary: $3100 / month (Gross)</p><p><br />🕒 Shift details:</p><p>10.5hrs / shift</p><p>24 days / month</p><p>6/5/6/5 working days / week</p><p>AM - 1030hrs - 2100hrs</p><p>PM - 1230hrs - 2300hrs</p><p>*1hr break included</p><p><br />📋 Requirements:</p><p>⁠Valid PLRD Security License</p><p>⁠⁠RTT/HCTA Certification</p><p>Neat & Presentable</p><p>Customer Service Oriented</p><p>⁠⁠⁠1 Notification Available</p><p><br />👔Dress Code (Not Provided)</p><p>Black Tie</p><p>Black Blazer</p><p>Black Collared Long Sleeve Button Down Shirt</p><p>Black Belt</p><p>Black Smart Pants</p><p>Black Smart Shoes</p><p>Black Socks (Above Ankle)</p><p><br />✨ Benefits:</p><p>Yearly Bonus Payout</p><p>Yearly Performance-Based Increment</p><p>Paid NTUC Union Membership</p><p>Birthday Leave (1 day)</p><p>Attractive Annual Leave Packages</p><p><br />🏣Office:</p><p>2 Sims Close</p><p>Gemini @ Sims  </p><p>#01-11/12</p><p>Singapore 387298<br /></p><p>If interested  please whatsapp:</p><p>📲Sylvester: +65 9136 1363</p><p>📲Dawnn: +65 8645 8667</p>",
